### Store Management API - Postman Collection

### 1. Login as Admin User
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Login as Staff User
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "staff",
  "password": "staff123"
}

### 3. Login with Invalid Credentials
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "invalid",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### 4. Login with Invalid Request Format
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "123"
}


### Variables for Postman Environment
# Set these in your Postman environment:
